{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L982"},"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","symbolKind":"method"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl","text":"UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}]}],"name":"annotation"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The control that was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"control"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"leftAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"rightAccessoryView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"text":"Related examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapViewDelegate"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutView":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNCalloutView","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol for a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclass that displays information about a selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation near that annotation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutview","fragments":[{"text":"MLNCalloutView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol"}}}